org.hl7.knowledgeartifact.r1

Class KnowledgeResource

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hl7.knowledgeartifact.r1.KnowledgeResource
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    InlineResource

    public class KnowledgeResource
extends Object
    KnowledgeResource specifies a reference to an associated resource of relevance to the artifact such as a guideline, a performance measure, another knowledge artifact, or a source of evidence for the artifact.

    Java class for KnowledgeResource complex type.
